import {Button, Modal} from "react-bootstrap";

let MyModal = ({showModal, setShowModal, state, setState}) => {
    console.log(state[showChangeDataModal.index])

    return (
        <Modal show={showModal} onHide={() => setShowModal({...showModal, visible: false})}>
            <Modal.Header closeButton>
                <Modal.Title>Change data</Modal.Title>
            </Modal.Header>
            <Modal.Body>Woohoo, you're reading this text in a modal!</Modal.Body>
            <Modal.Footer>
                <Button variant="secondary" onClick={() => setShowModal({...showModal, visible: false})}>
                    Close
                </Button>
                <Button variant="primary" onClick={() => setShowModal({...showModal, visible: false})}>
                    Save Changes
                </Button>
            </Modal.Footer>
        </Modal>
    )
}

export default MyModal;
